Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.38,0:00:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just my friend's letter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My very best friend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.34,0:00:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was 15
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us decided to cross the check border together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But my friend was captured
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And she was taken back to Prague
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She says she's doing fine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been such a good friend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows me better than my parents do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.51,0:00:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even my siblings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,With the government's tough inspections and censorship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what she went through to get this to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.73,0:00:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.50,0:00:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please visit me if you have the chance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I miss you so much my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.62,0:00:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Near cheddock Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside the three frogs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to call me by my real name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I am
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.13,0:01:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Helenka Novak
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.78,0:01:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For tonight I'm no longer Margo Langer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:03:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I sold my stock Holdings and Razer Burger Pharmaceuticals at the right time and then when I bought some
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking neuter Laboratories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really hit the jackpot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I wanted to celebrate so I did
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So you had a drink
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure just a little
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't too smart
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All I had was wondering what an alcoholic like yourself that was a foolish choice you made
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In your case it doesn't matter if you drink a little or a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing that concerns me is it seems you stopped going to your group meetings as well
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can keep a secret right
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got this special woman I want you to meet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you gone and found yourself another mistress
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really look this one's got a serious issue with alcohol
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's waiting just outside could you see her for a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't do counseling that way
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Have her make an appointment to see me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on just see her for a few minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making a house call next
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For a very important client
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a few days and went to Prague in the Czech Republic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it a very nice city to visit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Prague Castle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh and the wonderful Gothic cathedrals
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a beautiful place when the Old Town Plaza is all lit up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like a land out of a fairy tale
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What about sheddock Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you go and visit the chetak bridge I did
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly as you told me to do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,See I took a picture of the sign with the three frogs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And the woman was she there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No sir in fact no one was living there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately I didn't find any useful information for you by going there
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so frustrating
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't find Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Or any good leads on Dieter and Nina
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:05:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rabbit's foot
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for good luck
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now listen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give it to our child after it's born
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Margo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Helen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You must know
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me ma'am
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come from Germany and I'm searching for a missing woman who might have lived around here a while ago
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know young woman by the name of Margo Langer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait sorry her real name was helenka novakova
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Helenka
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway Mr schewald
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son Carl recently gave me a call
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He expressed some concerns to me about the fact that you haven't been eating properly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I classify that experience you had at the library fire as traumatic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A near-death experience can change one's life you know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense that paralyzing fear still hasn't left you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're very blessed to have Carl here with you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a wonderful thoughtful and loving son
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have nothing more to worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do try to eat regularly won't you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as that monster exists
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he know so much about Margo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could he have obtained all that information
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew much more than Carla I did
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Years ago Margo told me of this girlfriend she had who knew her even better than her own siblings
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember that conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the woman who Margo exchanged letters with now in the 1980s you began to search for Margo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time had gone missing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to Prague and actually met that woman didn't you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I did
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering she was supposed to be Margo's best friend I assume that woman might have heard something from her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she didn't know where Margo was
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But for a while we did talk quite a bit about Margo as we stood in the door
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,They were listening
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:07:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Listening in on every word
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you mean that quietly listen to what we said they stood behind the woman
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Absorbing it all those twins
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome have a seat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the young lady Mr thalbach wanted me to see aren't you and you're a compulsive drinker
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.04,0:08:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please just relax today all we're going to do here is have ourselves a nice friendly chat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it Meredith can't you see I'm right in the middle of a session
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a second repeating or breaking news story check police have Ann
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a witness and possible suspect in the poisoning of three doctors at dusseldorf's Isler Memorial Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.65,0:09:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He may also be connected with the murders of the journalist Maurer and the Fortner couple in Heidelberg and the Phantom killing at
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Heidelberg Castle
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,For now these are all the details we had him the police
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss heinemann
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being late everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why Mr Hess you look 10 years younger
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing with my grandchildren is keeping me young
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huber how you been
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually finishing up my final Academic Year
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you're pretty busy too Mr Kiefer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was bragging about you saying how I'm friends with a screenwriter who's going to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to catch the eye of a producer who has a big imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My first story idea is in development in my mind's brimming with new plot lines
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.18,0:09:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on your way no that's surgery saved my life
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If my surgery hadn't been a success I wouldn't be here to hear you laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And I never would have walked in the park with my grandchildren
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right there
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He always sat over there by himself drinking his tea
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Other doctors went to nicer cafes but he came here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it was closest to Eisler Memorial Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we patience would come in here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He would look at us as he sat there
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And smile at us
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the kindest doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A great doctor like him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He would never do this no
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the reason why I've gathered all of us here today
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The others who aren't here said they feel the same as we do
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After all they were doctor 10 most patients too
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:11:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad news Dr Schumann Mr Merkel just collapsed sir
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right over but I'm busy at the moment you better go and wait for me there all right
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Really
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr Tim I wouldn't do those things calm down and listen to me Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please dear go to him quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Picture I can't just
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you give me any butts Dr Tema has been charged with a crime he didn't commit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If he hadn't been around you know I wouldn't be alive right now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Dr Schumann are you so heartless that you don't want to help the man who saved your wife's life
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what will happen here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know darn well I'm the only doctor in this Village
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen to everyone that lives around here if I go and leave town
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.12,0:11:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go don't you quit your blabbering and get going right now Dr Tim I need your help
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I took an oath and if there's a patient who needs me I can't just leave him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way Dr Tema would have behaved
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please doctor would you see us now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Be patient I need a little more time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want to hurry up
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop your whining the doctor is taking a big risk by practicing without a license while she's going to school
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're in the darkness you only sink deeper into it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the lights shiny
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a real gift for this you'll make a fine doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right I'm ready to start now whoever's first come in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Lawyer right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But father wait
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have no way of knowing exactly where in Germany Tema will be sent then we'll have to retain a lawyer that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Like to defend him in any of the German states get us the best criminal attorney
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir we must have 10 I have the feeling that he is the only
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One who can do it he's the only one who can get rid of the monster
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We need strength in numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well let's try calling in more of doctor tennis former patients
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,As individuals what we say may not matter much
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But as a group we might just that's right
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask Isley Memorial Hospital for helping getting organized and we could ask them for funding too forget it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Isler Memorial Hospital is not about to help you with something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been listening to all of you and it's quite a touching story
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.21,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Really
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But come on folks
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Be realistic about the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.84,0:13:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the doctor Tema fan club going to prove his innocence
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr Becker it's you you know Tim I had no alibi and unfortunately he did have a motive
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The police even came out and said they found physical evidence at the scene of the crime
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you hire a brilliant lawyer to defend him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you gather a ton of people to make a lot of noise it's not going to help
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you folks do on Doctor 10 most behalf
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to prove that he's innoc
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I do ask you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real shame about his career
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real shame I'm going to ask you again Ava
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your relationship to Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Look Miss heinemann I don't know who you are in all of this but I'm on this train because
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuz I mean to save doctor Tenma so I don't want you coming along if you're here just to do some sightseeing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ava Heineman
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.61,0:15:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Heinemann Miss Heineman
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you are are you the daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr heinemann the murder director of that hospital in Dusseldorf
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr tema
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He had quite an effect on me you see he destroyed my life
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooking really save him now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw so what
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr Kenzo t
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Prime suspect in the serial murders in Dusseldorf and Heidelberg is still in custody in Prague
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Officials have said he will be extradited to Germany as soon as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He will most likely
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.58,0:15:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Dr Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who saved your life sick you're alive right now because of his first aid treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It turns out Dr 10 was also been framed for a crime he never committed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you two are in the same situation huh
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Save my life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to the same ordeal as me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a detective aren't you act like it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to calmly dissect and scrutinize everything there is really only one way to prevent yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,From being betrayed all you have to do is doubt the person you believe in the most
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to go
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to get to the Prague police station and talk to 10:00 no matter what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are sick
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective project
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please listen to me you don't have to run away anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My God you must have gone through a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been exonerated Sook
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The letter was sent to the station
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.91,0:17:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a copy of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a handwritten confession
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It has details of the events that only the killer would know
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've been cleared of all suspicion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who sent that letter
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.22,0:17:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A journalist who goes by the name of Grimmer
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say grandma
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah Grandma's been put on our most wanted list he's now our chief suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just hold on a second relax you're in the clear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector zamons murder the head Chiefs poisoning and the shooting of the two special team members that had tailed you back
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to your apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All those crimes are now solved
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:18:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well chief
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Was doing some sightseeing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.32,0:19:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit the ACT
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about Dr tema's arrest
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,10 mobile will be arriving at Dusseldorf tomorrow at 2:00 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're in charge of this case you'll need to meet the check police to take him into custody
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.56,0:19:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispatch someone else to take care of it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Prague is a very nice place
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please understand sir right now
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still on vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let me see Dr Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As I've been telling you sir you cannot see him
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And why not I thought this country is supposed to be a democracy doctor Tenma is already in the process
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being extradited to Germany I just need to see him for a minute
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We came on that way for nothing all that time and effort what a stupid waste let me see him
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,On your feet
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When we interrogate people what type of person do you think
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The hardest time
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,People who remain expressionless no matter what we say to them
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,People who don't say anything at all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the hardest kind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A love letter from the monster to the beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This appears to be a draft for a novel
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to devour you whole
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything about you consume me when I was falling apart how
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I look to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was falling apart the object you gave me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You left me a beautiful Jewel
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Those twins who look as if they are blessed with eternal life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.46,0:21:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The most sinful deed is to take away a person's name let's get your name back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:22:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you your name back your name is Anna
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now I'm sad sad sad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It exists
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.32,0:22:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many people that met their end in that room
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And then a horrific monster was born
